data.description: Looking for a beautiful home with a private fenced backyard perfect for entertaining? Look no further! This lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has just been listed in Commerce City Limits. With a spacious and well-maintained backyard, large deck you can enjoy summer barbecues, get togethers, or simply relax in your own private oasis. Storage shed in rear yard perfect for tools/lawn equipment! Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this charming home your own.
